 Nigerian Instagram sensation, Lekan Kingkong, recently took to social media to share the good news of him becoming a father with fans online. The proud new daddy took to his verified page on May 24, 2021, to share a photo of himself cradling his new born son and he sported a very big smile. In the caption of the post, the comedian explained how his son opened his eyes for the first time and how he would in turn love him till he closes his eyes. “You opened your eyes for the first time today my son, I will love you till the day I close mine and beyond. Kaabo Omo Ola. 24:05:2021”